            file:
                content: |
                    # Orchestra MCP Packs

                    This directory contains 17 installable packs of skills, agents, and hooks for Orchestra MCP projects.

                    Each subdirectory is a standalone GitHub repo, installable via:

                    ```bash
                    orchestra pack install github.com/orchestra-mcp/<pack-name>
                    ```

                    Or via the MCP `install_pack` tool.

                    ## Packs

                    | Pack | Stacks | Skills | Agents | Hooks |
                    |------|--------|--------|--------|-------|
                    | [pack-essentials](https://github.com/orchestra-mcp/pack-essentials) | * | project-manager, qa-testing, docs, plugin-generator | scrum-master, devops, qa-playwright | orchestra-mcp-hook |
                    | [pack-go-backend](https://github.com/orchestra-mcp/pack-go-backend) | go | go-backend | go-architect, qa-go | — |
                    | [pack-rust-engine](https://github.com/orchestra-mcp/pack-rust-engine) | rust | rust-engine | rust-engineer, qa-rust | — |
                    | [pack-react-frontend](https://github.com/orchestra-mcp/pack-react-frontend) | react, typescript | typescript-react, ui-design, tailwindcss-development | frontend-dev, ui-ux-designer, qa-node | — |
                    | [pack-database](https://github.com/orchestra-mcp/pack-database) | * | database-sync | dba, postgres-dba, sqlite-engineer, redis-engineer | — |
                    | [pack-ai](https://github.com/orchestra-mcp/pack-ai) | * | ai-agentic | ai-engineer, lancedb-engineer | — |
                    | [pack-mobile](https://github.com/orchestra-mcp/pack-mobile) | react-native | react-native-mobile | mobile-dev | — |
                    | [pack-desktop](https://github.com/orchestra-mcp/pack-desktop) | go | wails-desktop, macos-integration, native-widgets | platform-engineer, widget-engineer | — |
                    | [pack-extensions](https://github.com/orchestra-mcp/pack-extensions) | * | native-extensions, raycast-compat, vscode-compat, extension-marketplace | extension-architect | — |
                    | [pack-chrome](https://github.com/orchestra-mcp/pack-chrome) | typescript | chrome-extension | — | — |
                    | [pack-infra](https://github.com/orchestra-mcp/pack-infra) | docker | gcp-infrastructure | devops | — |
                    | [pack-proto](https://github.com/orchestra-mcp/pack-proto) | go, rust | proto-grpc | quic-protocol | — |
                    | [pack-native-swift](https://github.com/orchestra-mcp/pack-native-swift) | swift | — | swift-plugin | — |
                    | [pack-native-kotlin](https://github.com/orchestra-mcp/pack-native-kotlin) | kotlin, java | — | kotlin-plugin | — |
                    | [pack-native-csharp](https://github.com/orchestra-mcp/pack-native-csharp) | csharp | — | csharp-plugin | — |
                    | [pack-native-gtk](https://github.com/orchestra-mcp/pack-native-gtk) | c | — | gtk-plugin | — |
                    | [pack-analytics](https://github.com/orchestra-mcp/pack-analytics) | * | — | clickhouse-engineer | — |

                    ## Totals

                    - **22 skills** across 12 packs
                    - **26 agents** across 17 packs (devops appears in both essentials and infra)
                    - **1 hook** in pack-essentials

                    ## Publishing Updates

                    All 17 packs are published at [github.com/orchestra-mcp](https://github.com/orchestra-mcp). To push updates:

                    ```bash
                    cd packs/pack-go-backend
                    git add .
                    git commit -m "Update v0.2.0"
                    git push origin master
                    ```

                    ## Pack Format

                    Each pack must have a `pack.json` manifest:

                    ```json
                    {
                        "name": "orchestra-mcp/pack-go-backend",
                        "description": "Go backend skills and agents",
                        "version": "0.1.0",
                        "type": "pack",
                        "license": "MIT",
                        "stacks": ["go"],
                        "contents": {
                            "skills": ["go-backend"],
                            "agents": ["go-architect", "qa-go"],
                            "hooks": []
                        },
                        "tags": ["go", "backend"]
                    }
                    ```

                    Directory structure:
                    ```
                    pack-name/
                    ├── pack.json          # Required manifest
                    ├── README.md          # Pack documentation
                    ├── .gitignore
                    ├── skills/
                    │   └── skill-name/
                    │       └── SKILL.md   # Skill definition
                    ├── agents/
                    │   └── agent-name.md  # Agent definition
                    └── hooks/
                        └── hook-name.sh   # Hook script
                    ```
