                The tools.features plugin implements an 11-state feature lifecycle:

                ```
                backlog → todo → in-progress → ready-for-testing → in-testing →
                  ready-for-docs → in-docs → documented → in-review → done
                                                              │
                                      needs-edits ◄───────────┘
                ```

